WEBVTT

00:03.364 --> 00:05.704
You'll need to keep
an open mind over this.

00:06.484 --> 00:08.332
Suspend your disbelief.

00:09.164 --> 00:12.699
If I hadn't seen it with my own
eyes, I wouldn't believe it myself.

00:13.764 --> 00:15.984
There are times when I still don't.

00:17.404 --> 00:19.744
This is him before
everything unravelled.

00:19.764 --> 00:21.064
He was happy then.

00:21.564 --> 00:23.186
He didn't need to use it.

00:23.327 --> 00:25.979
If he did, it was
only when he was alone.

00:26.004 --> 00:29.059
Don't let the bugs bite, if
they do, squeeze them tight.

00:33.964 --> 00:35.291
Best boy.

00:39.685 --> 00:41.057
Door, Daddy.

00:42.364 --> 00:45.104
There's nothing in the dark
that's not there in the light, OK?

00:46.004 --> 00:48.940
Let's try and close it
for tonight, see how we go.

00:50.000 --> 00:56.074
